- insert new tree select count(*) from Claims_Template_Tree where App = 'CLAIMS' and Country_Id = ? and Lob_Id = ? and Template_Type_Id = ? -- if 0 then insert entry insert into Claims_Template_Tree (Template_Type_Id, App, Country_Id, Lob_Id) -- etc, and return key
-- insert new folder select tf.Id from Claims_Template_Folder tf join Claims_Template_Tree tt on tf.Tree_Id = tt.Id where tt.Country_Id = ? and tt.Lob_Id = ? and tt.Template_Type_Id = ? and tf.name = ? -- if 0 then insert entry insert into Claims_Template_Folder (Tree_Id, Name, Sort) -- etc with Tree_Id from previous query
-- insert new template -- tree and folder have been inserted or found, just insert with folder id
-- delete folder -- not allowed if not empty, else just delete
-- reorder folders -- update sorts on all folders for this tree according to new order
-- reorder templates in folder -- update sorts on all templates in this folder according to new order update Claims_Template t
